@startuml
actor Jeremy as "System Administrator"
participant System as "Kleff Hosting Platform"

Jeremy -> System : Request Cluster Health Dashboard
System -> System : Aggregating real-time metrics & logs

alt Success: Cluster Reachable
    System --> Jeremy : Display Dashboard (Full Metrics & Logs)
else API Timeout (Manual Screenshot Scenario)
    note right of System
        Logic: Go service returns partial data + warning logs
    end note
    System --> Jeremy : Display Dashboard with Partial Data / Loading Error
end

@enduml
